<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Most men have had the same old boring haircut since they were in middle school, but it’s time to grow up and step into the new year of 2022 with a fresh look.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>We’ve gathered 12 men’s haircut styles for you, from basic and low-maintenance to trendy and on-the-go. Whether you’re looking for a small update to your usual look or looking for a<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/grooming/">&nbsp;t</a><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.menstylists.com/mens-haircuts/" target="_blank">rendy haircut</a>&nbsp;to transform your look completely, this list of best&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/mens-haircuts/">men’s haircut styles</a>&nbsp;is sure to help you find some inspiration.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-1">Side Part</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/side-part-hairstyle.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/side-part-hairstyle.jpg" alt="Side Part Hairstyle"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Side Part Hairstyle</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The side part is one of understated Men’s Haircut Styles with tons of class, featuring&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/short-hairstyles-for-men/">short hair&nbsp;</a>combed over to one side in a deep part. A perfect choice for men with fine or thinning hair who want the volume to come mainly from their facial features instead of their hair.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The best&nbsp;<a href="https://supergreat.com/articles/holiday-gift-guide-haircare-must-haves-2021" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">hair care products</a>&nbsp;for this cut are&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/best-pomade-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">pomades</a>, especially those that have just a tiny bit of shine to them.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-2">Modern Pompadour</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/modern-pompadour-haircut.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/modern-pompadour-haircut.jpg" alt="modern pompadour haircut"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Modern Pompadour Men’s Haircut Styles</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/pompadour-haircuts/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">modern pompadour</a>&nbsp;is a variant of the classic style, with longer hair on top and shorter sides. It has a smooth fringe in front that adds an element of sophistication to your look.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Suitable for men who have thicker or wavier hair, this cut offers more styling options depending on what you want. You can make it look cleaner and more polished, or messy and textured for a disheveled finish that still looks good on your head.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This men’s haircut style works best for those who don’t mind styling their hair every day—an unstyled&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/pompadour-haircuts/">pompadour</a>&nbsp;just looks sad.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-3">Undercut plus Messy Hair on Top with a Long Fringe</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/hottest-undercut-hairstyle-trends.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/hottest-undercut-hairstyle-trends.jpg" alt=""/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Undercut plus Messy Hair – Men’s Haircut Styles</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/undercut-hairstyles-men/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">undercut</a>&nbsp;with fringe looks like a buzz cut at the bottom, but with the top kept long and flowing. This works best if you have thick hair, but can be done with thinner hair by using more product.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-4">Buzz Cut</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2005-Mens-Hairstyle-Buzzcut.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/2005-Mens-Hairstyle-Buzzcut.jpg" alt="2005 Mens Hairstyle Buzzcut"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Originally posted by Goodreads – Men’s Haircut Styles</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The buzz cut has been a popular men’s&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/military-haircut-styles/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">military haircut&nbsp;</a>style since WWII, and it still gets the job done today. All you need is to use some clippers with no guard attached to buzz all of your hair down to almost skin level.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-5">Short and Textured with a High Fade</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/high-fade-haircuts-2018.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/high-fade-haircuts-2018.jpg" alt="High Fade Haircuts"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Men’s Haircut Styles – Originally posted by&nbsp;<a href="https://www.pinterest.com/pin/440156563564610533/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Pinterest</a></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This cut features short textured hair on top that can be styled forward or messy, with a&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/fade-haircuts/">high fade</a>&nbsp;on the sides and back. It’s perfect for men who want a stylish but low-maintenance men’s haircut style.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-6">Straight and Brushed Back</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/thick-brushed-back-hairstyle-men.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/thick-brushed-back-hairstyle-men.jpg" alt="thick brushed back hairstyle men"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Men’s Haircut Styles – Originally posted by&nbsp;<a href="http://f.tqn.com/y/mensfashion/1/S/_/G/1/model-with-thick-brushed-back-hair.jpg" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">tqn</a></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Another relatively low-maintenance cut, this one features short hair brushed back to give it a smooth and shiny finish. It’s easy to style with just the fingers, so no need for expensive products or tools.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Suitable for men who have fine straight hair that doesn’t hold any kind of curl very well. Perfectly suitable if you want an office-appropriate look but still want to style your hair in a cool way.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-7">Short and Textured with a High Fade</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/short-mens-military-haircuts.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/short-mens-military-haircuts.jpg" alt="Short Mens Military Haircuts"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Short and Textured with a High Fade</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This haircut is perfect for men who want a low-maintenance style with plenty of edge. The hair on the top is styled short and textured, while the sides are cut very short into a high fade.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-8">Bro Flow</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/bro-flow.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/bro-flow.jpg" alt="bro flow"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Bro Flow Men’s Haircut Styles</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The bro flow is perfect for men who want a laid-back look with plenty of flow and movement. Thick medium-length wavy hair works best for this chill but rugged style. The bro flow is also a great option for men who want to grow their hair out.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-9">Two-Block Haircut</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/messy-haircuts-for-men-with-beard.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/messy-haircuts-for-men-with-beard.jpg" alt="messy haircuts for men with beard"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Originally posted by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.spentmydollars.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/hair-2Btrends-2Bmen-2B2015-2B2016-2Bhaircuts-2Bhairstyles-2B-3-.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">spentmydollars</a></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you or your girlfriend loves KPop then you need to try the two-block men’s haircut style. This style is inspired by&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/korean-hairstyle/">Korean hairstyles</a>&nbsp;and features short hair on the sides and back with long hair on top styled into two blocks or sections.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You can style the front and back if you want, but it’s not necessary. This cut is a great option for low-maintenance men who don’t want to use products to style their hair daily, while still having the option to dress it up from time to time.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-10">Shag</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Shaggy-cropped-haircut-for-men.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Shaggy-cropped-haircut-for-men.jpg" alt="Shaggy cropped haircut for men"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Originally posted by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.wlivenews.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Shaggy-crop.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">wlivenews</a></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you’re looking for something more funky and fashion-forward, the shag is a great option. This men’s haircut style features long hair on top that’s styled into loose waves and layers, while the sides are cut short into a fade or undercut.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The shag was especially famous in the 70s but has been experiencing a resurgence in recent years. If looking like a rockstar fits with your lifestyle, go for it!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-11">Quiff</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/womens-quiff-hairstyle.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/womens-quiff-hairstyle.jpg" alt="Quiff Hairstyle"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Quiff Hairstyle</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/mens-quiff-hairstyle/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">quiff</a>&nbsp;is another old-school men’s haircut style that’s experiencing a resurgence in popularity. It’s a variation of the pompadour, with more volume and height on top. It’s the cut most associated with James Dean and it’s perfect for men who want to complement their round faces with some volume at the hairline.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-12">French Crop</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/short-mens-haircuts-1.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/short-mens-haircuts-1.jpg" alt="Short Mens Haircuts"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">French Crop Hairstyle</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The French crop is a very short haircut that’s been gaining popularity in recent years. It features shorter hair on the sides and back with a long fringe or bangs in the front.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>You can style it messy or polished, but it’s best suited for men who have thick hair because thin hair might not hold its shape as well. This is a great option for men who want a stylish but low-maintenance men’s haircut style.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 id="ftoc-heading-13">Disconnected Undercut</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image {"linkDestination":"custom"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/disconnected-undercut.jpg"><img src="https://www.menstylists.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/disconnected-undercut.jpg" alt="Disconnected Undercut"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Originally posted by&nbsp;<a href="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/09/06/fashion/06NOTED1/06NOTED1-facebookJumbo.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">nyt</a></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The disconnected&nbsp;<a href="https://www.menstylists.com/undercut-hairstyles-men/">undercut</a>&nbsp;is a trendy and modern variation of the traditional undercut, featuring short hair on the sides and long hair on top that’s disconnected or styled into a messy fringe.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
